/CLAUDE.md
/AGENTS.md

# Editor / IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Per-developer Claude Code config
.claude/

# Container runtime data (SQLite, etc.)
deploy/load-balancer/data/

# Backup / scratch artefacts
*.bak
*.backup
*.backup-*

